  m_Name: Affection
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  defaultText: 'I would never be stingy with you! You''re dolphinately one of my
    favourite people, I''d never shy away from telling you how much I enjoy your
    company! Buuut right now I''m really hungry, so that kind of confession is going
    to have to wait!  '
